NBA potezi: Adetokunbo na čelu kolone, ali nije Janis! [VIDEO]
02 Nov 2019, 11:15 by Milos
NBA liga je izabrala 10 najboljih poteza sa mečeva igranih u noći između petka i subote.
Prvo mesto pripalo košarkašu Milvoki Baksa Tanasisu Adetokunbu, koji je je spektakularno zakucao u duelu protiv Indijane.
Uživajte i u majstorijama Džejsona Tejtuma, Džejmsa Hardena, Harisona Barnsa, Denija Grina, Aleksa Karuza, Derika Rouza…




POVEZANE OBJAVE
text:
NBA moves: Adetokunbo at the head of the column, but it's not Janis! [VIDEO]
02 Nov 2019, 11:15 by Milos
The NBA has selected the top 10 picks from matches played on a Friday to Saturday night.
The first place went to Milwaukee Bucks basketball player Tanasis Adetokunbu, who scored spectacularly in a duel against Indiana.
Enjoy the masters of Jason Tateum, James Harden, Harrison Barnes, Danny Greene, Alex Caruso, Derrick Rose…
